data.description: Nicely updated 3 bedroom 1 1/2 bath quad level home in Pine Island Ridge Subdivision. Remodeled kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, newer bamboo flooring throughout the home and wood burning fireplace. Upper level features 3 nice size bedrooms with jack and jill full main bath. 2 car attached garage, fenced yard with in ground pool for warm weather entertaining. All on a nice size corner lot.
